// availability. Covers come from libretro-thumbnails' Nintendo_-_Wii repo (Named_Boxarts/*(USA)*),
// not GameTDB's own art server -- that server stopped responding mid-pipeline (likely a rate-limit
// after the first verification pass) and never recovered in-session, so this GitHub mirror was used
// instead; see the `wii` registry entry for the covers-source note. `type` is 'retail' (disc),
// 'wiiware' or 'virtual_console' (WiiWare and VC are both Wii Shop Channel digital purchases, split
// because VC titles are emulated re-releases of pre-Wii games, not native Wii software). `genre` is
// GameTDB data mapped to this app's PT-BR taxonomy; a few titles GameTDB had no genre tag for are
// left empty (a real gap, not a guess). `localMP`/`players`/`online`/`motionPlus` come from
